{"content": "I need to multiply 321 \u00d7 760 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 321\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 1\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 1\u00d71 = 243 + 18 + 1 = 262\u2081\u2080\n- 760\u2089 = 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 6\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 7\u00d781 + 6\u00d79 + 0\u00d71 = 567 + 54 + 0 = 621\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 262 \u00d7 621 = 162,702\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 162702 \u00f7 9 = 18078 r 0\n- 18078 \u00f7 9 = 2008 r 6\n- 2008 \u00f7 9 = 223 r 1\n- 223 \u00f7 9 = 24 r 7\n- 24 \u00f7 9 = 2 r 6\n- 2 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 2\n\nReading from bottom to top: **267160\u2089**\n\n267160", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 344}